<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1920" height="1080"><rect width="1920" height="1080" fill="#0a0a0a"/><text x="960" y="120" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="36" fill="#ff4444">林家老宅门口</text><text x="960" y="300" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="48" fill="#fff">"滚！林家没你这个人！"</text><text x="960" y="380" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="36" fill="#aaa">——林家管家</text><rect x="400" y="440" width="1120" height="2" fill="#ff4444" opacity="0.5"/><text x="960" y="540" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="45" fill="#fff">林北掏出手机，拨了一个号码：</text><text x="960" y="640" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="55" fill="#ff4444">"十分钟内，我要见到林家家主。"</text><text x="960" y="760" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="40" fill="#aaa">电话那头：</text><text x="960" y="830" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="50" fill="#fff">"是！战神！"</text><rect x="0" y="950" width="1920" height="130" fill="rgba(255,0,0,0.1)"/><text x="960" y="1020" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="28" fill="#ff4444">管家还不知道，他刚刚骂了谁</text></svg>
